unded parts like a newborn baby before involving anyone else in their life.', 8163, 0), (220816, 'Divine self is holy being.', 2878, 0), (220817, 'I spent most of my adult life in relationships some good, some bad. It took years for me to realize that I was the common denominator in all of these relationships and I needed to love me first.', 8163, 0), (220818, 'Rags will never make fine clothing', 39441, 0), (220819, 'To find a happy ending with someone else, first you have to find it alone.', 7787, 0), (220820, 'All hatred of others is a reflection of self-hatred. All love of others is a reflection of self-love.', 4680, 0), (220821, 'Love does not envy, does not boast, does not delight in evil but rejoice in truth.', 2878, 0), (220822, 'The absence of self-love can never be replaced with the presence of people''s love for you.', 166, 0), (220823, 'I liked my face. Ethan liked my face. A lot of people liked my face. Besides, makeup was really just glorified face paint.', 39442, 0), (220824, 'The happiness you seek can be found within yourself.', 2878, 0), (220825, 'Love yourself and the beauty of your uniqueness.', 2878, 0), (220826, 'Nothing restricts your peace and happiness more than your limiting self-beliefs and fears.', 26483, 0), (220827, 'As days are numbered and life is short, why waste days feeling bad for yourself?', 15050, 0), (220828, 'People are beautiful. All people, of all shapes and sizes. The fact that we are living, breathing organisms that happen to have opposable thumbs, allowing us to pick up our phones and be on it for the entire damn day, is nothing short of brilliant. What makes us even more magnificent as a species is that we are lucky enough to be uniquely different - and it''s THAT individuality we must each harness and celebrate.', 1916, 0), (220829, 'A hateful heart is the greatest enemy of its self-love.', 166, 0), (220830, 'When your own approval means more than the approval of others, that is self-love.', 5084, 0), (220831, 'Refuse to worry. Cast your anxiety upon the Lord. He cares for you.', 2878, 0), (220832, 'The absence of unconditional self-love has led many people to sell themselves cheap.', 166, 0), (220833, 'If you are allowing something to upset or anger you, try this: Before giving in to those negative emotions, try and think of one positive thing, one learning that you will gain, a single glimpse of something that you can use to build a positive future. Here’s a nudge to push you along: You own your mind. You choose to be either a victim or to take control.', 12142, 0), (220834, 'The only love you should desperately search for, is the one that comes from you to you.', 166, 0), (220835, 'Start ignoring people who threaten your joy. Literally, ignore them. Say nothing. Don’t invite any parts of them into your space.', 10441, 0), (220836, 'Love yourself enough to have a meaningful life.', 25125, 0), (220837, 'No other love no matter how genuine it is, can fulfill one''s heart better than unconditional self-love.', 166, 0), (220838, 'Authenticity is not the search for uniqueness. An oak tree does not try to become an oak tree. A cactus does not try to become a cactus. All living things simply reach for nourishment - they reach for sun, reach for water, reach their roots deeper into the ground. By being open to receiving what they need, they become unique effortlessly. So let yourself fall open. Forget about crafting yourself a unique personality. Just allow. Allow in love. Allow pain. Allow desire. Allow learning. Allow healing. Allow frustration. Allow uncertainty. Allow yourself to experience what you must experience and learn what you need to learn, so that your uniqueness can emerge organically.', 5084, 0), (220839, 'When a witch embodies self-love, her energy becomes magnetic and her sense of possibility becomes contagious.', 21640, 0), (220840, 'No matter how stupid, how pointless, how painful my current situation was, as I listened to Mixtape every week I couldn''t deny the love 